# Agent Coding Standards

## Naming
Same as backend: PascalCase classes/methods, _camelCase fields, PascalCase properties.

## Async
All I/O operations must be async with CancellationToken.

## Win32 Interop
- Use `[DllImport]` or `[LibraryImport]` (.NET 7+ source gen)
- Always check return values
- Use `SafeHandle` for Win32 handles
- Dispose hooks on shutdown

## Logging
- Serilog with file sink (rolling daily, max 7 days)
- NEVER log: keystroke content, window titles (plaintext), photo data, JWT tokens
- DO log: event counts, sync status, errors, policy changes

## Error Handling
- Use try/catch around Win32 API calls (they can throw)
- Never crash the service — log and continue
- Use Polly for HTTP resilience
- Buffer data locally on any network failure
